Susan Silo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Silo 0 Susan Silo (born July 27, 1942 in New York City, New York) is an American singer and actress who is known for her work in voice over roles. Her first tv appearance was when she entered and won a contest over 350 people who auditioned across the US, at age 15, to sing (Mr. Wonderful) on The Jerry Lewis Show on November 5, 1957 which can be viewed on Amazon Prime Video episode 2.
